title: Unreal Engine 4.6 [Source + Optional] [soKuwaii]
description:
This torrent includes the following files:
>Optional.zip
>Required_1of2.zip
>Required_2of2.zip
>UnrealEngine-release.zip


Virus Scan: It's all source files, so I don't think this is needed

Installation:
>extract UnrealEngine-release-3.zip
>extract all other files
>open GenerateProjectFiles.bat
>wait for the prompt to finish and open UE4.sln

from there build the solution and open the binary by the name "UE4Editor.exe" found inside Engine/Binary/Win64(or 32 depending on build settings) as ADMINESTRATOR, and wait for it to finish the with the first time installation. After that it should work like a charm
